item.description:
arXiv:2409.05131v1 Announce Type: cross 
Abstract: In this paper, we aim to discuss three key questions:
  Q1. Justification of the model of relaxation time approximation (RTA) mathematically;
  Q2. Pole/cut structure in the retarded correlators within the kinetic description;
  Q3. Using only physical arguments and the eigenspectrum information of the linearized Boltzmann collision operator $\mathcal{L}_0$ defined in the main text to obtain the eigenspectrum properties of a class of redefined linearized collision operators.
